OL,3,CJersey's Chief Minister wants to stand
OL,4,Cwith Guernsey after ferry clash
OL,6,FIn another hearing a day later,
OL,7,FJersey's Sustainable Economic
OL,8,FDevelopment Minister, Deputy Kirsten
OL,9,FMorel, alleged that there had been a
OL,10,F"concerted effort in Guernsey" to
OL,11,F"talk down" DFDS in favour of Brittany
OL,12,FFerries.
OL,14,FIn a letter dated 24 March and
OL,15,Faddressed to Deputy Trott, Deputy
OL,16,FFarnham says: "The relationship
OL,17,Fbetween Jersey and Guernsey remains
OL,18,Fone that is highly valued, so I share
OL,19,Fyour regret that there has been a
OL,20,Fdifference of opinion between our
OL,21,Fislands.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
