PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1742912809
OL,3,CJersey's Chief Minister wants to stand
OL,4,Cwith Guernsey after ferry clash
OL,6,F"I agree with the sentiment in your
OL,7,Fletter that there is no profit to be
OL,8,Fgained for either island in a
OL,9,Fprotracted dissection of past comments
OL,10,For attempts to apportion blame. We
OL,11,Fmust move forward positively at both
OL,12,Fpolitical and officer level."
OL,14,FDirectly addressing comments made in
OL,15,Fthe recent hearings, Deputy Farnham
OL,16,Fadds: "The Jersey political system
OL,17,Fincludes a rigorous scrutiny process
OL,18,Fthat can be exacting, and ministers
OL,19,Fand officials have an obligation to
OL,20,Fanswer the questions directly and
OL,21,Fhonestly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
