CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1742912809
OL,3,CJersey's Chief Minister wants to stand
OL,4,Cwith Guernsey after ferry clash
OL,6,F"Sometimes this creates a spotlight
OL,7,Fthat is uncomfortable for all
OL,8,Fconcerned, but I would be surprised if
OL,9,Fthere were any intention other than to
OL,10,Fbe open in response to the scrutiny
OL,11,Fquestions.
OL,13,F"I have no doubt that the teams in
OL,14,Fboth Jersey and Guernsey have acted in
OL,15,Fgood faith to reach what they felt was
OL,16,Fthe right conclusion for their
OL,17,Frespective islands.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
