PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1742912809
OL,3,CJersey's Chief Minister wants to stand
OL,4,Cwith Guernsey after ferry clash
OL,6,F"I recognise your frustration about
OL,7,Fthe nature of the public debate, which
OL,8,Fonly highlights the economic and
OL,9,Fstrategic importance of our sea
OL,10,Fconnectivity and reflects the desire
OL,11,Fin both islands that we have strong,
OL,12,Fsustainable ferry links.
OL,14,F"I accept that comments have been made
OL,15,Fin both islands that have raised the
OL,16,Ftemperature, and I believe it is
OL,17,Fimportant that we, as Chief Ministers,
OL,18,Flead in building a more constructive
OL,19,Fdialogue.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
