OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1742912809
OL,3,CJersey's Chief Minister wants to stand
OL,4,Cwith Guernsey after ferry clash
OL,6,F"The public interest in our islands is
OL,7,Fbest served by drawing a line under
OL,8,Fevents and moving forward positively."
OL,10,FDeputy Farnham finishes his letter by
OL,11,Fhighlighting the cooperation between
OL,12,Fboth Bailiwicks on the international
OL,13,Fstage through their collaborative work
OL,14,Fon the British-Irish Council and their
OL,15,Fjoint offices in Brussels and Normandy.
